user.biography:
You might not know me yet, but I’m your newest BFF 👯‍♀️
Wife, mama, daughter of @lisafletcher805 😜
Grab a LDC & come be apart of our fam on Stories!

node.text: Here’s my kind of awk and super non-professional everyday makeup routine 😂 I should probably stick to 15 second story clips, but HEY! It was my first one, so cheers to trying new things 🥤 and adopting the IDGAF mentality 👊🏻😂💁‍♀️ lol if you saw my stories, you know 😉 Everything I used is linked on my blog with color info! 💕

node.text: Rhett turns one today! 🎉 He brings so much joy to everywhere he goes and is ALWAYS laughing! Becoming a mom completely changed me as a person, and I even though I literally still feel like I have no idea what I’m doing 😂 I love it more and more every single day! Happy FIRST birthday, buddy! 💛

node.text: Our home went on the market today and tbh I don’t feel “ready” to close that incredible chapter of our lives, but here I am. I talked about it on stories, but trusting God has bigger and better for you and stepping out of your comfort zone is scary and can be sad, but it doesn’t mean it’s wrong. Standing on that and encouraging you to go for it too because our potential and the greatness He has for us doesn’t lie in our comfort zones 💛 Here’s to bigger & better!

node.text:
A little dose of Instagram vs. reality for ya Dan’s been gone a whopping 6 hours 😜no worries! I’m holding down the fort just fine, babe 👍🏼 But I’m so stoked that @furbodogcamera gave me TWO Furbos to give away to you guys!! 🎉 It’s legit the greatest invention EVER! Dan got me this one for Christmas in 2013 😳🤣 and I have used it every day since 🙌🏼 if you’re a helicopter dog mom, you’re gonna freaking LOVE it!

To enter to win one:
1. Follow @furbodogcamera and @darylanndenner
2. Like this photo 👍🏼
3. Tag your friends! Each comment will be counted as 1 entry!
*Optional bonus entry: Share this to your story

WINNERS: @brianaols @breebarrette 🥳
